一、Requests库¶

$ pip3 install requests

（5）通用代码框架¶

Pythontry/excepttryexcept

In [13]:
import requests
def getHTMLText(url):
    try:
        r = requests.get(url, timeout = 30)
        r.raise_for_status()
        r.encoding = r.apparent_encoding
        return r.text
    except:
        return ""
if __name__=="__main__":
    url = "http://www.baidu.com"
    print(getHTMLText(url))

requests.request(method, url, kwargs) # kwargs:

params: url

data: Request

json: JSONRequest

http: HTTP

cookies: CookieJarRequestcookie

auth: HTTP

files:

timeout:

proxies:

（8）网络爬虫的限制¶

In [30]:
import requests
url = "https://item.jd.com/100012407280.html"
try:
    r = requests.get(url)
    r.raise_for_status()
    r.encoding = r.apparent_encoding
    print(r.text)
except:
    print("")

kv = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'}

try:
    r = requests.get(url, headers = kv)
    r.raise_for_status()
    r.encoding = r.apparent_encoding
    print(r.text)
except:
    print("")

        (function(cfg) {
            function setPlaceholder(val) {
                $('#key').val(val)
                .bind('focus',function(){
                    if (this.value==val){ this.value='';this.style.color='#333' }
                })
                .bind('blur',function(){
                    if (this.value==''){ this.value=val;this.style.color='#999' }
                });
            }
            function render(r) {
                if (!r || !r.length) return;
                var html = '';
                var el = document.getElementById('hotwords')

                for (var i = 0; i < r.length; i++) {
                    var item = r[i];

                    if (i === 0) {
                        setPlaceholder(item.name)
                    } else {
                        html += '<a target="_blank" data-id="'+ item.id +'" href="'+ item.url_info +'">'+ item.name +'</a>'
                    }
                }

                if (el) el.innerHTML = html
            }
            $.ajax({
                url: '//cds.3.cn/hotwords/get',
                data: { cate: cfg.cat.join(',') },
                dataType: 'jsonp',
                success: render
            })
        })(pageConfig.product);
    </script>

    function _seacrh_hot_keyword(obj){

<script>
    (function(cfg) {
        var $nav1 = $('#navitems-group1');
        var $nav2 = $('#navitems-group2');
        var html = '<li class="fore1" id="nav-home"> <a href="//www.jd.com/"></a> </li>';

        if (cfg.cmsNavigation && cfg.cmsNavigation.length && $nav1.length) {
            $nav2.html('');
            var corner_class = "";
            var corner_i="";
            for (var i = 0; i < cfg.cmsNavigation.length; i++) {
                var nav = cfg.cmsNavigation[i];
                if(nav.corner&&nav.corner!=""){
                    corner_class = "new-tab";
                    corner_i="<i class='icon-new'>"+nav.corner+"<span></span></i>";
                }else{
                    corner_class="";
                    corner_i="";
                }
                var j = i + 3;
                if(j.toString().length == 1) {
                    j = "0" + j;
                }
                html += '<li class="fore'+ i +' '+corner_class+'" clstag="shangpin|keycount|topitemnormal|c' + j + '">'+corner_i+'<a href="'+ nav.address +'" target="_blank">'+ nav.name +'</a> </li>';
            }

            $nav1.html(html);
        }
    })(pageConfig.product);
</script>

四、股票数据定向爬虫实例¶

1

     2

     3TXT

HTMLjavascriptrobots

In [95]:
import requests
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import traceback
import re
In [96]:
# URLURL
def getHTMLText(url):
    try:
        kv = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'}
        r = requests.get(url, timeout = 30, headers = kv)
        r.raise_for_status()
        r.encoding = r.apparent_encoding
        return r.text
    except:
        return ""
In [97]:
# lststockURLURLnumb
def getStockList(lst, stockURL, numb):
    html = getHTMLText(stockURL)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'html.parser')
    a = soup.find_all('a')
    count = 1
    for i in a:
        try:
            # 
            href = i.attrs['href']
            lst.append(re.findall(r"[s][hz]\d{6}", href)[0])
            count = count + 1
            if count > numb:
                break
        except:
            continue
In [98]:
# lststockURLURLfpath
def getStockInfo(lst, stockURL, fpath):
    for stock in lst:
        url = stockURL + stock
        html = getHTMLText(url)
        try:
            if html == "":
                continue
            infoDict = {}  # 
            soup = BeautifulSoup(html, 'html.parser')
            # 
            stockInfo = soup.find('div', attrs = {'class': 'stock-name'})
            name = stockInfo.string
            infoDict.update({'': name.split('(')[0]})
            infoDict.update({'': stock})
            # 
            stockInfo = soup.find('div', attrs = {'class': 'stock-current'})
            name = stockInfo.string
            infoDict.update({'': name.split('')[1]})
            # 
            stockInfo = soup.find('table', attrs = {'class': 'quote-info'})
            stockList = stockInfo.find_all('td')
            for i in range(len(stockList)):
                key = stockList[i].text.split('')[0]  # 
                val = stockList[i].text.split('')[1]
                infoDict[key] = val
            with open(fpath, 'a', encoding = 'utf-8') as f:
                f.write(str(infoDict) + '\n\n')
        except:
            traceback.print_exc()
            continue
In [103]:
def main():

    stock_info_url = 'https://xueqiu.com/S/'

    numb = 10
    slist = []

    getStockInfo(slist, stock_info_url, output_file)

In [118]:
def getHTMLText(url, code = 'utf-8'):
    try:
        kv = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'}
        r = requests.get(url, timeout = 30, headers = kv)
        r.raise_for_status()
        r.encoding = code
        return r.text
    except:
        return ""

五、修改User-Agent域依旧无法登陆怎么办？¶

https://juejin.im/post/5bd6acdbf265da0aba710136

In [ ]:
import requests
kv = {'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/66.0.3359.181 Safari/537.36'}
InfoURL = "https://www.amazon.cn/dp/B00NOQNHP2/ref=sr_1_1?__mk_zh_CN=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99&crid=1K8U4LVBU7N20&keywords=%E8%A7%A3%E5%BF%A7%E6%9D%82%E8%B4%A7%E9%93%BA&qid=1589337332&sprefix=jieyou%2Caps%2C165&sr=8-1"
try:
    r = requests.get(InfoURL, headers = kv)
    r.raise_for_status()
    r.encoding = r.apparent_encoding
    print(r.text)
except:
    print("")

1、post提交账户密码，请求登陆¶

session.post session.get HTML

import requests
headers = {
    'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/66.0.3359.181 Safari/537.36'
    }
data = {
    'identity':'',   
    'password':''    
}
LoginURL ='https://www.amazon.cn/ap/signin?_encoding=UTF8&openid.assoc_handle=cnflex&openid.claimed_id=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.identity=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.mode=checkid_setup&openid.ns=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0&openid.ns.pape=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fextensions%2Fpape%2F1.0&openid.pape.max_auth_age=0&openid.return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.cn%2Fgp%2Fyourstore%2Fhome%3Fie%3DUTF8%26action%3Dsign-out%26path%3D%252Fgp%252Fyourstore%252Fhome%26ref_%3Dnav_gno_signout%26signIn%3D1%26useRedirectOnSuccess%3D1'
InfoURL = 'https://www.amazon.cn/dp/B00NOQNHP2/ref=sr_1_1?__mk_zh_CN=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99&crid=1K8U4LVBU7N20&keywords=%E8%A7%A3%E5%BF%A7%E6%9D%82%E8%B4%A7%E9%93%BA&qid=1589337332&sprefix=jieyou%2Caps%2C165&sr=8-1'
try:
    session = requests.Session()
    session.post(LoginURL, headers = headers, data = data)
    # 
    r = session.get(InfoURL, headers = headers)
    r.raise_for_status()
except:
    print("")

def login():
    LoginURL ='https://www.amazon.cn/ap/signin?_encoding=UTF8&openid.assoc_handle=cnflex&openid.claimed_id=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.identity=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0%2Fidentifier_select&openid.mode=checkid_setup&openid.ns=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fauth%2F2.0&openid.ns.pape=http%3A%2F%2Fspecs.openid.net%2Fextensions%2Fpape%2F1.0&openid.pape.max_auth_age=0&openid.return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.cn%2Fgp%2Fyourstore%2Fhome%3Fie%3DUTF8%26action%3Dsign-out%26path%3D%252Fgp%252Fyourstore%252Fhome%26ref_%3Dnav_gno_signout%26signIn%3D1%26useRedirectOnSuccess%3D1'
    browser.get(LoginURL)
    input = browser.find_element_by_xpath("//*[@id='ap_email']");
    input.send_keys('')
    elem = driver.find_element_by_xpath("//*[@id='continue']");
    elem.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
    input = browser.find_element_by_xpath("//*[@id='ap_password']");
    input.send_keys('')
    elem = driver.find_element_by_xpath("//*[@id='auth-signin-button']");
    elem.send_keys(Keys.ENTER)
    get_page_index()

def get_page_index():
    InfoURL = "https://www.amazon.cn/dp/B00NOQNHP2/ref=sr_1_1?__mk_zh_CN=%E4%BA%9A%E9%A9%AC%E9%80%8A%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99&crid=1K8U4LVBU7N20&keywords=%E8%A7%A3%E5%BF%A7%E6%9D%82%E8%B4%A7%E9%93%BA&qid=1589337332&sprefix=jieyou%2Caps%2C165&sr=8-1"
    try:
        browser.get(InfoURL)
        print(browser.page_source)  # 
    except Exception as e:
        print(str(e))
